TITLE: Implementing the `set` method for a custom Seyfert Adapter
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to implement the `set` and `bulkSet` methods for a custom Seyfert adapter. The `set` method stores a key-value pair in the adapter's storage, and the `bulkSet` method iterates over an array of key-value pairs and calls `set` for each pair.
