TITLE: Implementing Data Deletion Methods in Seyfert Adapter in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet describes the implementation of `remove`, `bulkRemove`, and `flush` methods for a Seyfert adapter. The `remove` method deletes a single key, `bulkRemove` deletes multiple keys iteratively, and `flush` deletes both values and relationships associated with the adapter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tiramisulabs/seyfert-docs/blob/main/src/content/docs/recipes/cache.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
