TITLE: Handling Middleware Errors in Seyfert (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to handle errors caused by middleware stopping a Seyfert command. It uses the `@Middlewares` decorator to apply a middleware named "OnlyDev". The `onMiddlewaresError` method is overridden to display the middleware's error message to the user. Dependencies include `Command`, `Middlewares`, and `CommandContext` from "seyfert".
