TITLE: Filtering Component Interactions
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to filter component interactions based on the custom ID of the component. The `filter` method is overridden to check if the `customId` of the interaction matches 'hello-world'.  This ensures that the handler only processes interactions from the specified button.
