TITLE: Implementing Centralized Cache with WorkerAdapter
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to implement centralized cache management in Seyfert using the `WorkerAdapter`. It initializes a `WorkerClient`, sets up the cache service with the `WorkerAdapter`, passing the client's worker data for consistent data access across shards. This ensures that the cache is centralized in the main process.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tiramisulabs/seyfert-docs/blob/main/src/content/docs/es/recipes/sharding.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
